				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You have to code division routines yourself, the 6502 doesn't know how to do divisions or multiplications. Here's a page with tons of math routines: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://codebase64.org/doku.php?id=base:6502_6510_maths">http://codebase64.org/doku.php?id=base:6502_6510_maths</a><!-- m --><br /><br />You want to keep divisions and multiplications to a minimum in 6502 programs, since they're pretty slow compared to addition and subtraction.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
